(7, 1, '2015-09-03 17:07:41', '2015-09-03 17:07:41', 'The MGG FINE PIECE features an 18k Rose Gold plated Titanium nose bridge. The frame is constructed in full carbon fiber.\r\nAnd, the CR-39 lenses come in a polarized gray gradient with AR backing to ensure the best in visuals and sight protection. The 5 barrel, 18k rose gold plated hinges offer added comfort and soundness in structure.', 'MGG', '<h6 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #777777; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;">HANDCRAFTED ITALIAN CARBON FIBER &amp; 18K ROSE GOLD PLATED BRIDGE.</span></h6>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mgm', '', '', '2015-12-08 01:17:30', '2015-12-08 01:17:30', '', 0, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=7', 0, 'product', '', 0),
