(817, 161, '2015-12-12 03:14:33', '2015-12-12 03:14:33', '<div class="col-lg-6 talk">\r\n<div class="helo-outer">\r\n<div class="emailhello">EMAIL: <a href="mailto:INFO@DIROCCOEYEWEAR.COM">INFO@DIROCCOEYEWEAR.COM</a></div>\r\n<div>CALL: 305 965 4334</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-6 talk">\r\n<div class="helo-outer">You are browsing a creation that took over five years to develop. \r\n\r\nIn all of its complexities, carbon fiber has its own life. It will not bend to the will of the hands that shape it like metal, plastic, or acetate would. \r\n\r\nAt best, it will parlay before a true trixster and artisan; then unwillingly surrender to creation.\r\n\r\nAny divergence and slight differences are due to the artisanal production of this item. They are not to be considered imperfections, but like all creation, birthmarks that make them unique. \r\n\r\nYou and we are fortunate. The only thing it asks of us is to think of the time we have left on this planet and get busy living.  </div>\r\n</div>', 'Hello', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '113-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-12 03:14:33', '2015-12-12 03:14:33', '', 113, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/113-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
