(415, 158, '2015-11-16 17:28:03', '2015-11-16 17:28:03', '&nbsp;\r\n<div class="medium body-copy">\r\n<div class="block-content dynamic-text-left">\r\n<h2>The Brooklyn Circus + The Bearded Man.</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span class="drop-cap">M</span>r. Ouigi Theodore is a man of natural charisma. At first sight, his aesthetics scream Americana and a style reminiscent of an era when life took place, mostly, around the neighborhood; a time in NYC when blocks were entire cultures. The Brooklyn Circus is the embodiment of this, but most importantly, who he is at his core. With over a decade under his belt, Mr. Theodore, and his circus, are one of the most respected independent brands in the industry, who continuously influence bigger names like Opening Ceremony.\r\n\r\nTheir cult following is mostly present in Japan, Seoul (South Korea), and Italy. The Bk Circus is almost a must-visit for streetwise tourists who who flock to get a first hand look at the vibes of "The Bearded Man".\r\n\r\nFor us, The Brooklyn Circus stylishly defines the urban culture with its best foot forward. We hope to see Mr. Theodore continue to do for the urban culture in style, what Marvin Gaye did in music; or Jay-z, perhaps, in modern times.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-811" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/DIROCCO_EYEWEAR_TATANO_BK_CIRCUS_01.jpg" alt="DIROCCO_EYEWEAR_TATANO_BK_CIRCUS_01" width="2048" height="1363" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-812" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/DIROCCO_EYEWEAR_TATANO_BK_CIRCUS_06.jpg" alt="DIROCCO_EYEWEAR_TATANO_BK_CIRCUS_06" width="2048" height="1363" /></p>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-813" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/DIROCCO_EYEWEAR_TATANO_BK_CIRCUS_13a.jpg" alt="DIROCCO_EYEWEAR_TATANO_BK_CIRCUS_13a" width="2048" height="1363" /></p>', 'CIRCUS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-brooklyn-circus', '', '', '2015-12-15 17:45:12', '2015-12-15 17:45:12', '', 0, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/?p=415', 0, 'post', '', 0),
