(762, 161, '2015-12-14 22:53:54', '2015-12-14 22:53:54', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-740" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-013.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+013" width="2000" height="1334" />\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class="medium body-copy">\n<div class="block-content dynamic-text-left">\n<h2><span>MR. ROSS PINO &amp; HIS MANY BIKES</span></h2>\n&nbsp;\n<p><span class="drop-cap">M</span>r. Ross Pino is by far and away the real deal. As a model/actor he''s constantly used in photoshoots by brands who are looking to buy his look/story. He''s one of those men out there who is far from being a faker, and so, is why we are sharing his long journeyed story on our featured storytellers section.</p>\n<p>The pictures were taken by photographer @GlenAllsop</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-737" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-010.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+010" width="2000" height="1333" /></p>\n\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-742" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Unknown-2400x1600.jpeg" alt="Unknown" width="2400" height="1600" /></p>\n\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-738" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/CAFE-RACER-MOTO-glen-allsop-011.jpg" alt="CAFE+RACER+MOTO+(glen+allsop)+011" width="2000" height="1333" /></p>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/product/tatano/">Explore the TATANO frame</a></span><img class="aligncenter wp-image-442 size-full" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/TATANO_FRONT.jpg" alt="TATANO_FRONT" width="2400" height="2000" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Explore the TATANO frame</p>', 'DUST', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '418-