font-family: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Le Mans</em> was the very definition of a passion project for Mr McQueen, who, as well as being one of his generation’s most bankable box-office stars, was also a keen racing driver who had just placed second in the 12 Hours of Sebring endurance race in Florida. He envisaged it as the ultimate motor-racing movie, and a tribute to a sport that had always been close to his heart. Instead, it became, perhaps, his greatest folly.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="medium body-copy" style="margin: 0px 139.984375px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: WhitneyLight, WhitneyBook, Times, serif; line-height: inherit; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 679.984375px; float: left; color: #2b2b2b; letter-spacing: 0.23999999463558197px;">\r\n<div class="block-content dynamic-text-left" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p style="margin: 0em 0px 1.76471em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: 1.76471em; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: baseline;">“I don’t think there’s any racing driver that can really tell you why he races. But I think he can probably show you.” These words, spoken by the man himself, are taken from a new documentary, <a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #2b2b2b; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" href="http://www.themanlemans.com/" target="_blank"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Steve McQueen: The Man And Le Mans</em></a>, that attempts to tell the true story of how the movie was made – and the unseen effects that its disaster-ridden produ