://dev.hungrylemur.com/product/lola/"><strong> Explore the LOLA</strong></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p class="story-photos"><img class="alignnone wp-image-428 size-full" src="http://dev.hungrylemur.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/LOLA_ANGLE.jpg" alt="LOLA_ANGLE" width="2400" height="2000" /></p>', 'RUNNING', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-15 05:08:10', '2015-12-15 05:08:10', '', 41, 'http://dev.hungrylemur.com/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
